OL,3,CCrash victim's family speak of
OL,4,Cheartbreak as road death figure rises
OL,6,FThe family of a teenager who died in a
OL,7,Fcollision near Castlewellan have said
OL,8,Fthey now understand the devastation
OL,9,Fcaused such tragedies.
OL,11,FJay Marks from Downpatrick, was killed
OL,12,Fafter his car left the Ballylough Road
OL,13,Fon 2 February. Despite efforts from
OL,14,Femergency services to save his life,
OL,15,Fhe died at the scene.
