OL,3,CCrash victim's family speak of
OL,4,Cheartbreak as road death figure rises
OL,6,FThe 18-year-old is one of 16 victims
OL,7,Fkilled on Northern Ireland's roads in
OL,8,F2024, the highest number for eight
OL,9,Fyears. Half of these deaths have
OL,10,Foccurred in the south east region,
OL,11,Facross County Down and County Armagh.
OL,13,FSpeaking exclusively to UTV, his
OL,14,Fmother Donna and sister Leasa, said
OL,15,FJay will never be forgotten and that
OL,16,Ftwo months on, things are still
OL,17,Fdifficult.
OL,19,F"Last week and this week has been the
OL,20,Fhardest for me I think," said Leasa.
