OL,4,Cheartbreak as road death figure rises
OL,6,F"You're throwing yourself into doing
OL,7,Feverything for him, you know, the
OL,8,Ffuneral and the month's mind and
OL,9,Fthings like that. And now you're just
OL,10,Flike, what do you do now?"
OL,12,F75% of road deaths so far have
OL,13,Foccurred on rural roads, just as Jay's
OL,14,Fdid as he made his way home from work.
OL,16,F"He (Patrick, Jay's father) saw the
OL,17,Ftwo air ambulance guys jumping over
OL,18,Fthe fence and coming down towards us
OL,19,Fand he said, 'Donna, I think we've
OL,20,Flost Jamie."
