OL,3,CCrash victim's family speak of
OL,4,Cheartbreak as road death figure rises
OL,6,FDavy Jackson, Chairman of Road Safe NI
OL,7,Fsaid he was 'very dismayed' at the
OL,8,Fnumber of road deaths.J"Last year we
OL,9,Fhad 71 which was the highest figure
OL,10,Ffor over 8 years.J"Sadly this year has
OL,11,Fstarted off much the same. On the
OL,12,Ffourth of this month we were on 15.
OL,13,FSame as last year.J"So it looks like
OL,14,Fthe number is going to be high this
OL,15,Fyear unless people change their ways."
OL,17,FOonagh Burns from Strabane is the
OL,18,Flatest person to be killed on our
OL,19,Froads. The 35-year-old died on the A5
OL,20,Fon Sunday leaving yet another family
OL,21,Fin mourning.
